Explanation:

We iterate through each character in the text string and check if it is present in the set of broken characters. If a character is not in the set, it means it is a valid character that can be used, so we increment the count. The time complexity is O(n) because we iterate through the text string once, and the space complexity is O(n) as we create a set with n elements.

